          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.opencompute.org/marketplace\"><strong>OCP Marketplace</strong></a> 是查詢<strong>經認證的硬體</strong>、<strong>軟體</strong>和<strong>設施</strong>的中心平臺。它不只是目錄，更是與<strong>解決方案提供商</strong>建立聯絡的重要工具；這些提供商可以幫助您把<strong>開放技術</strong>整合到具體環境中。<br><br>無論您需要<strong>ORv3 機架</strong>還是<strong>完整解決方案</strong>，Marketplace 都能幫助您與可信、經過驗證的供應商合作。</p><p>單擊標記，進一步瞭解各個類別。</p>"
