        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "heading_paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>部署步驟</p>",
          "body_html": "<p>採用開放基礎設施是一個戰略過程。 <br><br>請遵循以下關鍵步驟以確保平穩過渡：</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "process",
          "variant": "process",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "intro",
              "title": "介紹",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>瞭解有效採用和實施該框架的基本步驟。 遵循這些準則可確保平穩過渡和最佳結果。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "評估",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>評估當前的<strong>工作負載</strong>、<strong>功率限制</strong>和<strong>散熱挑戰</strong>，瞭解起點並確定需要改進的領域。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "確定方案",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>使用 <strong>OCP Marketplace</strong> 查詢符合具體<strong>密度</strong>和<strong>運營要求</strong>的<strong>硬體解決方案</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "建立合作",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>與<strong>OCP 解決方案提供商</strong>合作，制定符合您需求的完整<strong>整合計劃</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "部署",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>先開展<strong>小規模實施</strong>，例如部署<strong>單個機架</strong>或<strong>試點艙</strong>，再擴充套件到<strong>整個設施</strong>。</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "summary",
              "title": "總結",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>透過遵循這些步驟，您可以有效地採用該框架並自信且高效地實現您的目標。</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
